Can We Finally Stop Doing Things 'Backwards And In Heels'?
"She was doing everything I was doing," he said, "but just like Ginger Rogers, it was backwards in heels."
Now, it's always great to hear the leader of the free world acknowledge the unlevel playing field ... but I have one quibble: I think it's time we stopped talking about women doing things "backwards and in high heels."
"But if you give us a chance, we can perform," she said, and then delivered the "backwards and in high heels" line with gusto to thunderous applause.
"Only I had to do it, you know, backwards and in high heels after I'd had hair and makeup done."